                    <li>
                        Lists -> Product
                        <br />
                        Products or Service you sell. For Example: Pen, Jacket, Printer etc
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Lists -> PriceBook
                        <br />
                        PriceBook or PriceList is the list which contains prices of the products
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Add all the product you need to sell in your “Price Book” by going to “Price Book Details” page and click on “Add” button and adding prices. These prices can be modified when used in an “Opportunity”, “Quote” or “Order”.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        You cannot access a “Product” directly into an “Opportunity”, “Quote” or “Order”. You can access a “Product” only via a “PriceBook”.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        You can access a “PriceBook” directly from “Opportunity Detail” or “Quote Detail” or “Order Detail” by clicking “Add” link (in bottom) on respective detail page in respective “Opportunity Line Item” or “Quote Line Item” or “Order Line Item” section.
                    </li>
